---
import TerminalBlock from "./TerminalBlock.astro";
---

<section id="slash" class="relative py-32">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute -left-24 top-1/3 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-sky-400/12 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute -right-24 bottom-1/4 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-orange-500/12 blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6">
    <div class="grid items-center gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
      <div class="order-2 animate-slide-up lg:order-1" style="opacity: 0;">
        <TerminalBlock title="Slash command flow">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <div style="color: #c6ae90;">
                <span class="text-green-400">$</span>
                <span class="text-amber-100"> /deploy</span>
              </div>
              <div class="pl-4" style="color: #c6ae90;">
                <span class="text-amber-300">Parameters:</span>
                <span class="text-cyan-200"> environment, tag</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div style="color: #c6ae90;">
                <span class="text-green-400">$</span>
                <span class="text-amber-100"> /deploy staging, v1.24.0</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-1 text-green-300/80">
                &#10003; Script executed and output returned in launcher
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div style="color: #c6ae90;">
                <span class="text-green-400">$</span>
                <span class="text-amber-100"> /summarize-pr</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-1 text-cyan-200/80">
                Not found &rarr; Buddio asks your agent to create it
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </TerminalBlock>
      </div>

      <div class="order-1 animate-slide-up lg:order-2" style="animation-delay: 0.1s; opacity: 0;">
        <div
          class="mb-4 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-launcher-accent/25 bg-launcher-accent/10 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-launcher-accent"
        >
          Slash Commands
        </div>

        <h2 class="section-heading mb-6">
          Fast actions with
          <span class="gradient-text">"/"</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="mb-6 text-lg text-launcher-muted">
          Buddio&apos;s slash command mode gives you a fast path from intent to script execution,
          with discoverable commands and parameter hints built into the launcher.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          {[
            "Type '/' to browse or filter available commands in real time",
            "Use Enter to open parameter mode with live parameter hints",
            "Run scripts directly and capture command output in the launcher",
            "If no command exists, Buddio can ask your AI agent to create one",
          ].map((text) => (
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-launcher-muted">
              <div class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-launcher-accent" />
              <span>{text}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
